NK002(kha)011:1: gyi khyad par rgyas pa'i gzungs bklag pa'i cho ga
NK002(kha)011:2: mdo sde las btus pa bzhugs so //
NK002(kha)011:3: de bzhin gshegs pa bdun gyi sngon gyi smon lam
NK002(kha)011:4: gyi khyad par rgyas pa'i gzungs bklag pa'i cho ga
NK002(kha)011:6: de bzhin gshegs pa bdun la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK002(kha)011:8: lus legs par bkrus la gos bzang po dri ma med pa bgo zhing /
NK002(kha)011:9: kha zas gtsang ma bza' bar bya /
NK002(kha)011:10: sems nyon mongs pa la sogs pa'i dri ma med par byas te /
NK002(kha)011:11: dkon mchog gsum gyi yon tan dang /
NK002(kha)011:12: mdo sde'i phan yon la yid ches shing /
NK002(kha)011:13: dad pa dang gus pa bskyed /
NK002(kha)011:15: khyim pa yin na bsnyen gnas kyi khrims bzung /
NK002(kha)011:16: dus bzang po tshes brgyad lta bu la brtsam /
NK002(kha)011:17: de nas yid du 'ong ba gtsang mar byas la /
NK002(kha)011:18: gdugs dang rgyal mtshan mang pos legs par brgyan pa'i nang du /
NK002(kha)011:19: sa gzhi spos kyi man+dala chen po byas la /
NK002(kha)011:21: me tog gis bkram par bya'o //
NK002(kha)011:23: 'jim pa las byas pa yang rung ste /
NK002(kha)011:24: ring bsrel dang bcas pa bya /
NK002(kha)011:26: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i gdan yang bsham /
NK002(kha)011:27: mchod pa ci 'byor pa yang bsham ste /
NK002(kha)011:28: sku gzugs re re'i spyan sngar mar me bdun bdun
NK002(kha)011:29: dang tshon sna lnga pa'i ba dan bdun bdun bzhag
NK002(kha)011:34: rin po che sna bdun dang /
NK002(kha)011:36: bum pa la sogs pa sta gon bya'o //
NK002(kha)011:37: mdo sde 'di dang shes rab kyi pha rol du
NK002(kha)011:38: phyin pa la sogs pa mdo sde zab cing rgya
NK002(kha)011:39: che ba gzhan yang ci nus kyis bklag /
NK002(kha)011:40: gzungs kyis cho ga 'di zhag bdun nam /
NK002(kha)011:43: bzhi bcu rtsa dgu snyed du bklag par bya'o //
NK002(kha)011:44: de ltar mchod pa bshams pa dang /
NK002(kha)011:45: dge 'dun tshogs nas stan bde ba la 'dug nas /
NK002(kha)011:46: stong pa nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin ni ci nus su bsgom /
NK002(kha)011:47: de las langs nas sems can thams cad kyi don du tshad med pa bzhi bsgom zhing /
NK002(kha)011:48: byang chub kyi sems yid la bya /
NK002(kha)011:49: de ltar rang gi nus pa dang phyogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa sras dang bcas pas /
NK002(kha)011:50: de ltar byin gyis rlabs par yang bsam /
NK002(kha)011:51: de nas gnas byin gyis rlabs par bya ste /
NK002(kha)011:52: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa dang /
NK002(kha)011:53: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyi byin gyi rlabs dang /
NK002(kha)011:54: tshogs gnyis yongs su rdzogs pa'i mnga' thang chen po dang /
NK002(kha)011:55: chos kyi dbyings rnam par dag cing bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i stobs kyis /
NK002(kha)011:56: de bzhin gshegs pa bdun gyi sngon gyi smon lam
NK002(kha)011:57: gyi khyab par rgyas pa'i mdo las byung ba'i cho
NK002(kha)011:58: ga bzhin / phyogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa sras dang bcas pa dang /
NK002(kha)011:59: 'phags pa dam pa chos skyong ba thams cad gdan 'dzom pa'i pho brang gi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK002(kha)011:60: mchod pa'i tshogs sbyar ba 'di rnams /
NK002(kha)011:61: ji ltar sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' de
NK002(kha)011:62: dag gi sngon gyi smon lam khyad par can gyis
NK002(kha)011:63: bsgrubs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing yongs su dag pa
NK002(kha)011:64: dang / bcom ldan 'das 'od dpag med kyi zhing
NK002(kha)011:65: gi bkod pa'i yon tan lta bu dang ldan par
NK002(kha)011:66: dang / gyur te / sa gzhi rin po che
NK002(kha)011:67: sna tshogs kyi rang bzhin lag mthil ltar mnyam pa
NK002(kha)011:68: dang / gyur te / / thag gru che ba /
NK002(kha)011:69: yangs pa reg na 'jam zhing bde ba /
NK002(kha)011:70: dri ma med cing 'od gsal ba /
NK002(kha)011:71: tsan dan sbrul gyi snying po'i dri bsung dang ldan
NK002(kha)011:72: pa lha'i me tog sna tshogs kyis gcal du bkram
NK002(kha)011:73: pa / mtha' rin po che'i pha gus brtsigs pa /
NK002(kha)011:75: mu tig gi phye ma gram bur bdal ba /
NK002(kha)011:78: pad+ma 'gying zhing ldem pas khebs par gyur cing /
NK002(kha)011:79: chu bya sna tshogs skad snyan par sgrog pa /
NK002(kha)011:80: dga' zhing 'phyo la lding bas brgyan pa'i yan lag
NK002(kha)011:81: brgyad dang ldan pa'i mtsho dang rdzing dang lding ka
NK002(kha)011:82: dag gis mdzes par byas pa /
NK002(kha)011:83: rin po che'i dpag bsam gyi shing ljon pa /
NK002(kha)011:86: rin po che 'phyang pa me tog gi mgo lcogs dang /
NK002(kha)011:87: 'bras bu mdzes par chags pas g.yur za zhing ldem pa /
NK002(kha)011:88: gser gyi dril bu g.yer kha 'khrol ba las dam
NK002(kha)011:89: pa'i chos kyi sgra 'byung ba dang ldan pa tshar
NK002(kha)011:90: du sbrengs pas legs par brgyan pa'i sa gzhi la
NK002(kha)011:91: / gzhal med khang chen po rin po che sna bdun mchog tu 'bar ba bkod pa /
NK002(kha)011:92: 'jig rten gyi khams dpag tu med pa rgyas par
NK002(kha)011:93: 'gengs pa'i 'od zer chen po rab tu 'byung ba
NK002(kha)011:94: gnas tha dad pa shin tu rnam par bye ba
NK002(kha)011:95: mtha' yas pa rnam par gnas pa /
NK002(kha)011:96: rgya yongs su ma chad pa /
NK002(kha)011:97: khams gsum las yang dag par 'das pa'i spyod yul
NK002(kha)011:98: 'jig rten las yang dag par 'das pa de'i bla
NK002(kha)011:99: ma'i dge ba'i rtsa ba las byung ba /
NK002(kha)011:100: shin tu rnam par dag cing dbang bsgyur ba'i rnam par rig pa'i mtshan nyid /
NK002(kha)011:102: byang chub sems dpa'i dge 'dun dang ldan pa /
NK002(kha)011:103: lha dang klu dang gnod sbyin dang dri za dang lha ma yin dang /
NK002(kha)011:107: mi dang mi ma yin pa mtha' yas par rnam
NK002(kha)011:108: par rgyu ba chos kyi ro'i dga' ba dang bde
NK002(kha)011:110: sems can thams cad kyi don thams cad yang dag par thob par byed pas nye bar gnas pa /
NK002(kha)011:111: nyon mongs pa'i gnod pa'i dri ma thams cad dang bral ba /
NK002(kha)011:112: bdud thams cad yongs su spangs pa /
NK002(kha)011:113: thams cad kyi bkod pa las lhags pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa'i bkod pa'i gnas dran pa dang /
NK002(kha)011:115: rtogs pa chen pos nges pa 'byung ba zhi gnas dang lhag mthong gi bzhon pa yin pa /
NK002(kha)011:116: rnam par thar pa'i sgo stong pa nyid dang /
NK002(kha)011:117: mtshan ma med pa nyid dang /
NK002(kha)011:118: smon pa med pa nas 'jug pa /
NK002(kha)011:119: rin po che'i pad+ma'i rgyal po /
NK002(kha)011:120: yon tan mtha' yas pas brgyan pa'i bkod pa las
NK002(kha)011:121: brten pa'i gzhal med khang chen por gyur pa'i dbus
NK002(kha)011:122: su / pad+ma'i gdan rin po che'i seng ge'i khri'i steng la /
NK002(kha)011:123: de bzhin gshegs pa mtshan legs par yongs bsgrags dpal gyi rgyal po dang /
NK002(kha)011:124: de bzhin gshegs pa rin po che dang zla ba
NK002(kha)011:125: dang pad+mas rab tu brgyan pa mkhas pa gzi brjid
NK002(kha)011:126: sgra dbyangs kyi rgyal po dang /
NK002(kha)011:127: de bzhin gshegs pa gser bzangs dri med rin chen snang ba brtul zhugs grub pa dang /
NK002(kha)011:128: de bzhin gshegs pa mya ngan med mchog dpal dang /
NK002(kha)011:129: de bzhin gshegs pa chos bsgrags rgya mtsho'i dbyangs dang /
NK002(kha)011:130: de bzhin gshegs pa chos rgya mtsho mchog gi blos rnam par rol pas mngon par mkhyen pa dang /
NK002(kha)011:131: de bzhin gshegs pa sman gyi bla bee d+aur+ya 'od kyi rgyal po dang /
NK002(kha)011:132: bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa la sogs pa phyogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa dang /
NK002(kha)011:134: 'phags pa dam pa'i chos skyong ba thams cad gdan 'dzom pa'i bzhugs gnas /
NK002(kha)011:135: 'phags pa so so'i smon lam khyad par can dang /
NK002(kha)011:136: mnga' thang dang 'tsham par grub pa mdzes pa sha stag 'byung bar gyur cig /
NK002(kha)011:137: phyi nang kun tu yang cha rigs dang 'tsham par
NK002(kha)011:138: yang lha dang mi'i yo byad dam pa zhal zas
NK002(kha)011:139: dang na bza' dang rgyal mtshan dang rol mo la
NK002(kha)011:140: sogs pa phul du phyin pa sna tshogs phung po
NK002(kha)011:142: bzang po spyod pa'i smon lam las byung ba'i mchod
NK002(kha)011:143: pa'i sprin rgya mtsho thams cad kyis rgyas par gang
NK002(kha)011:144: zhing rgyan klubs pa dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK002(kha)011:145: 'phags pa thams cad kyang gdan 'dzom nas de bzhin
NK002(kha)011:146: du byin gyis brlabs shing bzhes te longs spyod par
NK002(kha)011:147: gyur cig / ces lan gsum du bzlas /
NK002(kha)011:148: yang dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa dang /
NK002(kha)011:149: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyi byin gyis rlabs dang /
NK002(kha)011:150: tshogs gnyis yongs su rdzogs pa'i mnga' thang chen po dang /

NK002(kha)011:165: pa phyogs bcu na dus gsum du bzhugs pa'i de

NK002(kha)011:168: byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs dang bcas pa thams cad bdag cag la dgongs su gsol /

NK002(kha)011:171: dam pa'i chos ltar bcos pa 'byung ba na sems
NK002(kha)011:172: can las kyi sgrib pa sna tshogs kyis bsgribs pa

NK002(kha)011:174: mya ngan dang sdug bsngal sna tshogs kyis gtses pa /
NK002(kha)011:175: phongs par gyur pa'i sems can thams cad rjes su bzung zhing lha dang mi rnams kyi don dang /
NK002(kha)011:176: phan pa dang bde ba'i slad du /
NK002(kha)011:177: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi thabs mkhas pa mang po dang /
NK002(kha)011:178: sngon gyi smon lam gyi khyad par rgyas pa bzang zhing rlabs che ba /

NK002(kha)011:184: pa chen po mdzad de byin gyis rlabs par ci

NK002(kha)011:186: rgyas bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa gdul bya'i dbang
NK002(kha)011:187: gis 'dzam bu'i gling 'dir mya ngan las 'das pa'i
NK002(kha)011:188: tshul bstan kyang 'jig rten gyis khams gzhan du de

NK002(kha)011:190: 'gro ba'i don mdzad cing bzhugs pa yang de bzhin

NK002(kha)011:192: las khyad par can las glengs te /
NK002(kha)011:193: bdag cag rnams mnga' ris kyi gdul bya rnams phyag mtshan du bzhes pa'i nang du gtogs te /
NK002(kha)011:194: bka' drin thob pa'i 'phro mchis pa tsam la bstan te /
NK002(kha)011:195: che ge mo la sogs pa 'gro ba mang po

NK002(kha)011:199: chen po mdzad de byin gyis rlabs par ci gnang
NK002(kha)011:200: / byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po 'phags pa 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa dang /
NK002(kha)011:201: rgyal ba'i sras po skyabs grol dang /
NK002(kha)011:202: phyag na rdo rje la sogs pa byang chub sems
NK002(kha)011:203: dpa' sems dpa' chen po gang dag sngon de bzhin
NK002(kha)011:204: gshegs pa bdun gyi sngon gyi smon lam gyi khyad
NK002(kha)011:205: par rgyas pa'i mdo bka' brtsal pa'i tshe gdan 'dzom
NK002(kha)011:206: par 'dus te / mdo'i don byin gyis brlabs shing /
NK002(kha)011:207: de bzhin gshegs pa'i bka' bsgrub par thugs bskyed pa

NK002(kha)011:209: ba mang po bskyabs pa'i slad du mgon skyabs dang
NK002(kha)011:210: dpung gnyen du spyan 'dren zhing mchis na /

NK002(kha)011:227: che ge mo la sogs pa 'gro ba mang po bskyab pa'i slad du /
NK002(kha)011:228: mgon skyabs dang dpung gnyen du spyan 'dren cing mchis na /
NK002(kha)011:229: mchod pa'i tshogs sbyar ba'i pho brang gi dkyil 'khor
NK002(kha)011:230: 'dir gshegs shing gdan 'dzom pa chen po mdzad de
NK002(kha)011:231: byin gyis rlabs par ci gnang /
NK002(kha)011:232: sngon de bzhin gshegs pa gdan 'dzom pa'i spyan sngar /
NK002(kha)011:233: de bzhin gshegs pa bdun gyi sngon gyi smon lam
NK002(kha)011:234: gyi khyad par rgyas pa'i mdo sde 'chang ba dang
NK002(kha)011:235: mchod pa la sogs pa'i sems can de dag phyag

NK002(kha)011:592: 'dzin dang dran pa dang stobs dang gzungs kyi sgo
NK002(kha)011:593: rnams dang byang chub kyi yan lag rnams mngon du
NK002(kha)011:594: gyur cig / shes rab chen po rjes su rgyu bar gyur cig /
NK002(kha)011:595: bdag cag la sogs pa sems can gang dag dman
NK002(kha)011:596: pa la mos shing nyan thos kyi theg pa dang
NK002(kha)011:597: rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa la 'dod pa bskyed
NK002(kha)011:598: de / de la gnas shing bla na med pa
NK002(kha)011:599: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub la rgyab kyis
NK002(kha)011:600: phyogs par gyur pa de dag thams cad byang chub
NK002(kha)011:601: kyi mthar thug gi bar du bla na med pa
NK002(kha)011:602: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub las phyir mi
NK002(kha)011:604: nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas kyi sa las yang dag par 'das par gyur cig /
NK002(kha)011:605: byang chub kyi sems yid la byed pa dang mi 'bral bar gyur cig /
NK002(kha)011:606: bdag cag la sogs pa sems can gang dag bskal pa chen po zad pa'i tshe /
NK002(kha)011:607: 'dzam bu'i gling kun tu 'bar zhing rab tu 'bar
NK002(kha)011:608: ba 'khrugs par gyur te ngu zhing mya ngan byed
NK002(kha)011:609: la / sngon gyi mi dge ba'i las kyi rgyus
NK002(kha)011:610: sdug bsngal 'byung zhing skyabs med mgon med pa de
NK002(kha)011:611: dag thams cad sdug bsngal dang mya ngan dang bral
NK002(kha)011:612: la / bar gyur cig / bsil ba'i dngos po thob par gyur cig /
NK002(kha)011:613: shi 'phos nas kyang bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs
NK002(kha)011:614: pa rin po che dang zla ba dang pad+mas rab
NK002(kha)011:615: tu brgyan pa mkhas pa gzi brjid sgra dbyangs kyi
NK002(kha)011:616: rgyal po'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing rnam par dag par
NK002(kha)011:617: pad+ma'i snying po seng ge'i khri la rdzus te skye
NK002(kha)011:618: bar gyur cig / skyes ma thag tu gzungs dang
NK002(kha)011:619: ting nge 'dzin la sog sa pa yon tan gyi
NK002(kha)011:620: tshogs thams cad mngon du gyur te /
NK002(kha)011:621: ston pa bla na med pa rin po che dang
NK002(kha)011:622: zla ba dang pad+mas rab tu brgyan pa mkhas pa
NK002(kha)011:623: gzi brjid sgra dbyangs kyi rgyal po la sogs pa
NK002(kha)011:624: bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad las bka' lung yang dag
NK002(kha)011:625: par nod thugs mnyes par byed cing /
NK002(kha)011:626: skad cig skad cig la sangs rgyas kyi zhing thams
NK002(kha)011:627: cad du thogs pa med par 'jug par gyur cig
NK002(kha)011:628: / bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom
NK002(kha)011:629: pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas gser bzangs
NK002(kha)011:630: dri med rin chen snang brtul zhugs grub pa la
NK002(kha)011:631: / phyag 'tshal lo // mchod do skyabs su mchi'o //
NK002(kha)011:634: deng rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa'i tshogs gdan 'dzom
NK002(kha)011:635: pa'i spyan sngar de bzhin gshegs pa gser bzangs dri
NK002(kha)011:636: med rin chen snang ba brtul zhugs grub pa'i mtshan
NK002(kha)011:637: yid la dran zhing lan bdun brjod pa dang phyag
NK002(kha)011:638: 'tshal zhing mchod pa la sogs pa'i mthus /
NK002(kha)011:639: de bzhin gshegs pa gser bzangs dri med rin chen
NK002(kha)011:640: snang ba brtul zhugs grub pa de'i sngon gyi smon

NK002(kha)011:642: sogs pa sems can gang dag srog gcod pa /
NK002(kha)011:643: mi dge ba'i las rnam pa sna tshogs byed pa /
NK002(kha)011:644: srog chags sna tshogs kyi srog gcod pa'i las byas
NK002(kha)011:645: pas tshe thung zhing nad mang ba dang chu dang
NK002(kha)011:646: dug dang mtshon dang me dang nad sna tshogs kyis

NK002(kha)011:648: sgrib pa de dag thams cad yongs su byang ste
NK002(kha)011:651: su yang dus ma yin par 'chi ba'i dus byed par ma gyur cig /

NK002(kha)011:654: gyi rdzas brkus phrogs pas dbul por skyes te sgren

NK002(kha)011:656: gdungs shing sdug bsngal myong ba de dag thams cad
NK002(kha)011:657: 'phral du sdig pa thams cad byang ste /
NK002(kha)011:658: byang chub kyi mthar thug gi bar du dbang phyug
NK002(kha)011:659: phun sum tshogs shing ma tshang ba med pa thob
NK002(kha)011:660: par gyur cig / bdag cag la sogs pa sems
NK002(kha)011:661: can gang dag gcig la gcig gnod sems dang lngan
NK002(kha)011:662: zhing phan tshun srog gcod par byed pa dang /
NK002(kha)011:663: 'thab par byed pa de dag thams cad bla na
NK002(kha)011:664: med pa'i byang chub tu sangs rgyas kyi bar du
NK002(kha)011:665: phan tshun pha ma ltar byams pa la gnas par
NK002(kha)011:666: gyur cig / bdag cag la sogs pa sems can gang dag 'dod chags dang zhe sdang dang /
NK002(kha)011:668: tshul khrims 'chal bar gyur nas sdig pa kun tu spyod cing bslabs pa dral la /
NK002(kha)011:669: dad pas byin pa longs spyod pas ngan song gsum
NK002(kha)011:670: du ltung zhing sems can dmyal bar 'gro bar 'gyur
NK002(kha)011:671: ba de dag thams cad 'phral du las kyi sgrib
NK002(kha)011:672: pa thams cad yongs su byang bar gyur cig /

NK002(kha)011:675: tshul khrims yang dag par 'dzin cing lus dang ngag
NK002(kha)011:676: dang yid sdom pa la gnas par gyur cig /
NK002(kha)011:677: byang chub kyi sems yid la byed pa dang mi 'bral bar gyur cig /

NK002(kha)011:688: a ma le bi ma le dril med dril ma /

NK002(kha)011:695: mchog gi rnams sgrub byed pa /
NK002(kha)011:704: b+hi ta b+ha yangs 'jigs byed 'jigs pa'i su bar+ne mdog legs ma /

NK002(kha)011:717: phyag 'tshal ba yi gzhi tshugs shig /
NK002(kha)011:718: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa gser bzangs dri
NK002(kha)011:719: med rin chen snang ba brtul zhugs grub pa des
NK002(kha)011:720: byang chub kyi shing drung du bzhugs te /
NK002(kha)011:724: nad sna tshogs kyis gzir ba /
NK002(kha)011:725: 'chi ba dang dgra dang dgon pas gnod par gyur pa /
NK002(kha)011:726: tshe bskal par thub pa'i sems can dmyal ba gzhol ba'i sems can rnams gzigs nas /
NK002(kha)011:727: de dag gi don du sangs rgyas kyi byang chub la 'god pa dang /

NK002(kha)011:731: can thams cad kyi mtshams med pa lnga la sogs
NK002(kha)011:732: pa sdig pa thams cad byang bar gyur cig /

NK002(kha)011:735: med rin chen snang ba brtul zhugs grub pas dgongs

NK002(kha)011:760: med mchog dpal de'i sngon gyi smon lam khyad par

NK002(kha)011:924: gsad pa'i 'os su gyur pa de dag thams cad byang chub kyi mthar thug gi bar du /

NK002(kha)011:926: bla na med pa'i rang dbang phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK002(kha)011:927: bdag cag la sogs pa sems can gang tshe thung
NK002(kha)011:928: bar 'gyur ba'i sdig pa mi dge ba sna tshogs
NK002(kha)011:929: byas te / 'chi bar 'gyur ba de dag thams
NK002(kha)011:930: cad sdig pa'i las thams cad yongs su byang ste
NK002(kha)011:931: byas te / / tshe ring zhing dus ma yin par 'chi bar 'gyur pas /
NK002(kha)011:932: nam yang 'ga' yang 'chi bar ma gyur cig /
NK002(kha)011:933: 'chi kar yang de bzhin gshegs pa chos rgya mtsho
NK002(kha)011:934: mchog gi blos rnam par rol pa mngon par mkhyen
NK002(kha)011:935: pa'i mtshan rna lam du grag cing /
NK002(kha)011:936: rjes su dran nas bde 'gro mtho ris kyi 'jig rten tu skyes bar gyur cig /
NK002(kha)011:937: byang chub kyi mthar thug gi bar du lha dang mi'i bde ba myong bar gyur cig /
NK002(kha)011:938: 'di nas shi 'phos nas kyang bcom ldan 'das de
NK002(kha)011:939: bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs
NK002(kha)011:940: pa'i sangs rgyas chos rgya mtsho mchog gi blos rnam
NK002(kha)011:941: par rol pa mngon par mkhyen pa'i sangs rgyas kyi
NK002(kha)011:942: zhing du pad+ma'i snying po seng ge'i khri la rdzus
NK002(kha)011:943: te skye zhing / skyes ma thag tu gzungs dang /
NK002(kha)011:944: ting nge 'dzin la sogs pa'i yon tan gyi tshogs thams cad mngon du gyur te /
NK002(kha)011:945: ston pa bla na med pa chos rgya mtsho mchog
NK002(kha)011:946: gi blos rnam par rol pas mngon par mkhyen pa
NK002(kha)011:947: la sogs pa phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad las
NK002(kha)011:948: bka' lung yang dag par nod thugs mnyes par byed
NK002(kha)011:949: cing / skad cig skad cig la sangs rgyas kyi
NK002(kha)011:950: zhing thams cad du thogs pa med par 'jug par
NK002(kha)011:951: cing / gyur cig / bcom ldan 'das de bzhin
NK002(kha)011:952: gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i
NK002(kha)011:953: sangs rgyas sman gyi bla beed+aur+ya 'od kyi rgyal po
NK002(kha)011:957: skabs 'dir mchod pa ci 'byor pa dbul /
NK002(kha)011:958: deng rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa'i tshogs gdan 'dzom pa'i spyan sngar /
NK002(kha)011:959: de bzhin gshegs pa sman gyi bla beed+aur+ya'i 'od kyi rgyal po'i mtshan thos te /
NK002(kha)011:960: yid la dran zhing lan bdun brjod de /
NK002(kha)011:961: phyag 'tshal zhing mchod pa la sogs pa'i mthus /
NK002(kha)011:962: de bzhin gshegs pa sman gyi bla bee d+aur+ya'i 'od
NK002(kha)011:963: kyi rgyal po de'i sngon gyi smon lam khyad par
NK002(kha)011:965: bdag cag la sogs pa sems can thams cad skyes bu chen po'i mtshan sum cu rtsa gnyis dang /
NK002(kha)011:966: dpe byad bzang po brgyad cus legs par brgyan par gyur te /
NK002(kha)011:967: bdag ci 'dra ba de bzhin du sems can thams cad kyang de 'dra bar gyur cig /
NK002(kha)011:968: lus kyi 'od zer gyis 'jig rten gyi khams grangs
NK002(kha)011:969: med pa dpag gis mi lang ba dag lham me
NK002(kha)011:970: lhan ne lhang nger gyur cig /
NK002(kha)011:971: lus nor bu rin po che bee d+aur+ya ci 'dra
NK002(kha)011:972: ba de 'dra bar phyi nang shin tu yongs su
NK002(kha)011:973: dag pa dang / dri ma med la 'od gsal ba dang /
NK002(kha)011:974: kho lag yangs shing che ba dang /
NK002(kha)011:975: dpal dang gzi brjid 'bar ba dang /
NK002(kha)011:977: nyi ma dang zla ba las lhag pa'i 'od zer
NK002(kha)011:978: kyi dra ba rnams kyis legs par brgyan par gyur
NK002(kha)011:979: cig / de bzhin gshegs pa sman gyi bla beed+aur+ya'i
NK002(kha)011:980: 'od kyi rgyal po ci 'dra ba de 'dra bar
NK002(kha)011:981: cig / gyur te / sems can gang dag 'jig rten gyi bar dag tu skyes pa dag dang /
NK002(kha)011:982: gang dag yang mi'i 'jig rten 'di na mtshan mo
NK002(kha)011:983: mun pa mun nag gi nang na phyogs tha dad
NK002(kha)011:984: par 'gro ba de dag bdag gi 'od kyis phyogs
NK002(kha)011:985: dga' mgur 'gro zhing las rnams kyang byed par gyur
NK002(kha)011:986: cig / de bzhin gshegs pa sman gyi bla bee
NK002(kha)011:987: d+aur+ya'i 'od kyi rgyal po de'i shes rab dang thabs
NK002(kha)011:989: bdag cag la sogs pa sems can gyi khams dpag
NK002(kha)011:990: gis mi lang ba dag longs spyod zad mi shes
NK002(kha)011:991: pa dang ldan par gyur te /
NK002(kha)011:992: su yang cig kyang brel ba med par gyur cig /
NK002(kha)011:993: bdag cag la sogs pa sems can gang dag lam ngan par zhugs pa dang /
NK002(kha)011:995: rang sangs rgyas kyi lam du zhugs pa de dag
NK002(kha)011:996: thams cad theg pa chen po bla na med pa'i
NK002(kha)011:997: lam la zhugs par gyur cig /
NK002(kha)011:998: bdag cag la sogs pa sems can thams cad byang
NK002(kha)011:999: chub kyi mthar thug gi bar du sdom pa gsum
NK002(kha)011:1001: tshul khrims nyams pa med par gyur cig /
NK002(kha)011:1002: su yang tshul khrims log par zhugs te /
NK002(kha)011:1004: bdag cag la sogs pa sems can gang dag lus ngan pa dang /
NK002(kha)011:1005: dbang po ma tshang ba dang /
NK002(kha)011:1016: lus la nad kyis btab pa de dag thams cad
NK002(kha)011:1017: las kyi sgrib pa thams cad byang nas thams cad
NK002(kha)011:1018: dbang po tshang zhing yan lag yongs su rdzogs par
NK002(kha)011:1019: gyur cig / bdag cag la sogs pa sems can gang dag nad sna tshogs kyis gzer ba /
NK002(kha)011:1026: sdug bsngal ba de dag gi nad thams cad rab tu zhi bar gyur cig /
NK002(kha)011:1027: byang chub kyi mthar thug gi bar du nad med cing gnod pa med pa dang /
NK002(kha)011:1028: yo byad phun sum tshogs pa la gnas par gyur cig /
NK002(kha)011:1029: bud med gang dag bud med kyi skyon brgyad dag gis kun nas nyon mongs par gyur pa /
NK002(kha)011:1030: bud med kyi dngos po la mi dga' ba /
NK002(kha)011:1031: bud med kyi skye gnas las thar bar 'dod pa
NK002(kha)011:1032: de dag thams cad bud med kyi dngos po las
NK002(kha)011:1034: byang chub kyi mthar thug gi bar du skyes pa'i dbang po dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK002(kha)011:1035: bdag cag la sogs pa sems can thams cad bdud
NK002(kha)011:1036: kyi zhags pa las yongs su thar bar gyur cig
NK002(kha)011:1037: / lta ba tha dad pa mi mthun pa zing
NK002(kha)011:1038: zing bas mi mthun pa dag spangs te yang dag
NK002(kha)011:1039: pa'i lta ba la gnas par gyur cig /
NK002(kha)011:1040: byang chub kyi spyod pa rlabs po che yongs su rdzogs par gyur cig /
NK002(kha)011:1041: bdag cag la sogs pa sems can gang su dag rgyal po'i 'jigs pas skrag pa dang /
NK002(kha)011:1042: gang dag bcing ba dang rdeg pa dang go rar gzhug pa dang gsad par 'os pa /
NK002(kha)011:1043: rgyu du mas kun tu gtses pa /
NK002(kha)011:1045: lus dang ngag dang sems sdug bsngal gyis nyan pa de dag bdag gi bsod nams kyi mthus /
NK002(kha)011:1046: gnod pa thams cad las yongs su thar bar gyur cig /
NK002(kha)011:1047: bdag cag la sogs pa sems can gang dag bkres pa dang skom pa'i me rab tu 'bar ba /
NK002(kha)011:1048: kha zas 'tshol ba la rab tu brtson pa /
NK002(kha)011:1049: sdig pa'i las byed pa de dag bdag gis kha
NK002(kha)011:1050: dog dang dri dang ror ldan pa'i bza' btung gis
NK002(kha)011:1051: tshim par byas te phyis chos kyi ros shin tu
NK002(kha)011:1052: bde ba la 'god par gyur cig /
NK002(kha)011:1053: bdag cag la sogs pa sems can gang dag sgren mo bgo ba med pa dbul ba /
NK002(kha)011:1055: grang ba dang tsha ba dang sbrang bu dang /
NK002(kha)011:1056: sha sbrang dag gis nyin mtshan du sdug bsngal gyi
NK002(kha)011:1057: tshor ba myong ba de dag bdag gis gos yongs
NK002(kha)011:1059: tshon sna tshogs su kha bsgyur ba dag dang rin
NK002(kha)011:1060: po che'i rgyan dang spud pa dang phreng ba dang
NK002(kha)011:1061: byug pa dang rol mo'i sgra dang sil snyan dang
NK002(kha)011:1062: phag rdob pa rnams kyis sems can rnams kyi bsam
NK002(kha)011:1063: pa thams cad yongs su rdzogs par gyur cig /
NK002(kha)011:1064: 'phags pa dgyes pa'i tshul khrims kyi dga' ba dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK002(kha)011:1065: nyon mongs pa'i gdung bas mi rdzi bar rnam par grol ba'i bde ba la gnas par gyur cig /
NK002(kha)011:1066: 'di nas shi 'phos nas kyang de bzhin gshegs pa
NK002(kha)011:1067: sman gyi bla bee d+aur+ya'i 'od kyi rgyal po'i sangs
NK002(kha)011:1068: rgyas kyi zhing du pad+ma'i snying po seng ge'i khri
NK002(kha)011:1070: skyes ma thag tu gzungs dang ting nge 'dzin la
NK002(kha)011:1071: sogs pa yon tan gyi tshogs thams cad mngon du
NK002(kha)011:1072: gyur te / ston pa bla na med pa sman
NK002(kha)011:1073: gyi bla bee d+aur+ya'i 'od kyi rgyal po la sogs
NK002(kha)011:1074: pa phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad las bka' lung
NK002(kha)011:1077: skad cig skad cig la sangs rgyas kyi zhing thams
NK002(kha)011:1078: cad du thogs pa med par 'jug par gyur cig
NK002(kha)011:1079: / ston pa bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa
NK002(kha)011:1080: dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK002(kha)011:1081: dpal rgyal ba sh+aakya thub pa la phyag 'tshal lo
NK002(kha)011:1084: skabs 'dir gong bzhin mchod pa ci 'byor pa dbul /
NK002(kha)011:1085: deng rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa'i tshogs gdan 'dzom
NK002(kha)011:1086: pa'i spyan sngar de bzhin gshegs pa sh+aakya thub pa'i
NK002(kha)011:1087: mtshan yid la dran zhing lan bdun brjod de phyag
NK002(kha)011:1088: 'tshal zhing mchod pa la sogs pa'i mthus /
NK002(kha)011:1089: ston pa de bzhin gshegs pa sh+aakya thub pas bdag
NK002(kha)011:1090: cag la sogs pa sems can gang dag las kyi
NK002(kha)011:1091: sgribs pa sna tshogs kyis sgribs pa /
NK002(kha)011:1092: nad sna tshogs kyis gzir ba /
NK002(kha)011:1093: mya ngan dang sdug bsngal sna tshogs kyis gtses pa /
NK002(kha)011:1094: phongs par gyur pa'i sems can thams cad rjes su
NK002(kha)011:1095: gzung zhing lha dang mi rnams kyi don dang sman
NK002(kha)011:1096: pa dang bde ba'i slad du de bzhin gshegs pa
NK002(kha)011:1097: bdun gyi thabs mkhas pa dang sngon gyi smon lam
NK002(kha)011:1098: gyi khyad par rgyas pa byin gyis rlabs zhing dpal
NK002(kha)011:1099: gyi mgul nas 'di skad du 'jam dpal de ltar
NK002(kha)011:1100: bas na / yon tan thams cad don du gnyer
NK002(kha)011:1101: ba rnams kyis nyon mongs pa dang ma 'dres par
NK002(kha)011:1102: de bzhin gshegs pa bdun gyi mtshan bzung bar bya
NK002(kha)011:1103: bas na / / nyin lan gsum mtshan lan gsum du yid la bya /
NK002(kha)011:1106: me tog dang bdug pa dang mar me dang byug
NK002(kha)011:1107: pa dang zhal zas dang rol mo'i sgra la sogs
NK002(kha)011:1109: yan lag brgyad dang ldan pa'i bsnyen gnas la nye bar gnas par bya /
NK002(kha)011:1110: nyin bdun gtsang mar byas te sa phyogs gtsang mar
NK002(kha)011:1111: gnas shing sangs rgyas kyi zhing der skye bar smon
NK002(kha)011:1113: sems can thams cad la byams pa dang snying rje'i
NK002(kha)011:1114: sems su bya zhes bya ba la sogs pa dang
NK002(kha)011:1121: sab+ta ta th+aa ga ta sa m+aad+h+ya d+hish+thi te /
NK002(kha)011:1125: sarba p+aa pam n+aa sha ya /
NK002(kha)011:1129: bud+d+ha k+she tra pa ri sho d+ha ni /
NK002(kha)011:1134: sarba a k+aa la mri t+yu ni b+aa ra ni /
NK002(kha)011:1135: bud+d+he su bud+d+he bud+d+ha a d+hish+thi na /
NK002(kha)011:1137: bdag la bsrung bar mdzad du gsol /
NK002(kha)011:1139: mi mnyam mnyam pa'i sa me a pa me /
NK002(kha)011:1142: bdag la dgongs par ha ran tu me /
NK002(kha)011:1145: sangs rgyas byang chub bo d+hi sat+w+aa nam /
NK002(kha)011:1148: zhi ma zhi ma pra sha man+tu me /
NK002(kha)011:1150: sarba shin tu 'tsho ba'i i t+yu pa t+r+aa ba /
NK002(kha)011:1152: b+y+aa d+ha yahp+au ra ni rdzogs shing rdzogs par p+au ra ni /
NK002(kha)011:1155: bdag gi bsam pa sarba +aa sh+aa ye /
NK002(kha)011:1157: bee d+aur+ya beed+aur+ya'i pra ti b+h+aa se /
NK002(kha)011:1159: sarba sdig kun zad pa'i p+aa pam k+sha yang+ka ri s+w+aa h+aa /
NK002(kha)011:1161: bee d+aur+ya'i 'od ces bya ba'i gzungs 'di /
NK002(kha)011:1162: rigs kyi bu'am rigs kyi bu mo gang la la zhig gis /
NK002(kha)011:1166: lan stong rtsa brgyad du bton na /
NK002(kha)011:1167: de la de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis dgongs par 'gyur /
NK002(kha)011:1168: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyis sems par 'gyur /
NK002(kha)011:1169: rdo rje 'dzin pa thams cad kyis yang dag par bsrung bar 'gyur /
NK002(kha)011:1173: rgyal po chen po bzhi dag gis kyang yongs su bskyang bar 'gyur /
NK002(kha)011:1174: mtshams med pa lnga la sogs pa las kyi sgrib pa thams cad kyang yongs su byang bar 'gyur /
NK002(kha)011:1175: nad thams cad kyis mi btab par 'gyur /
NK002(kha)011:1177: dus ma yin par 'chi ba'i 'jigs pa thams cad las yongs su thar par 'gyur /
NK002(kha)011:1182: 'gyed pa thams cad rab tu zhi bar gyur /
NK002(kha)011:1183: dgra thams cad kyi dbang du 'gro bar mi 'gyur
NK002(kha)011:1184: ci bsam pa thams cad yongs su rdzogs par 'gyur
NK002(kha)011:1185: ro // zhes ji skad bka' bstsal pa de dag
NK002(kha)011:1186: thams cad che ge mo la sogs pa'i don du
NK002(kha)011:1187: mdo las byung ba'i cho ga bzhin du /
NK002(kha)011:1188: de bzhin gshegs pa bdun dang /
NK002(kha)011:1189: ston pa bde bar gshegs pa rnams gdan 'dzom pa'i
NK002(kha)011:1190: spyan sngar mchod cing smon lam gsol ba dang gzungs
NK002(kha)011:1191: sngags bzlas pas ci ltar byin gyi brlabs shing bka'
NK002(kha)011:1192: bstsal ba bzhin du byin gyis rlabs cing /
NK002(kha)011:1193: phan yon ji skad bka' bstsal pa thams cad bdag
NK002(kha)011:1194: cag la sogs sems can thams cad kyis 'phral du
NK002(kha)011:1195: thob par mdzad cing bstsal bar ci gnang /
NK002(kha)011:1196: ma rig mun sel sgron me'i mchog /
NK002(kha)011:1197: sdug bsngal nad sel sman gyi phul /
NK002(kha)011:1198: dam chos dkon mchog thams cad la //
NK002(kha)011:1199: phyag 'tshal mchod cing skyabs su mchi //
NK002(kha)011:1201: skabs 'dir mchod pa ci 'byor pa dbul /
NK002(kha)011:1202: de bzhin gshegs pa'i bka' yang dag pa tshad mar gyur pa /
NK002(kha)011:1203: 'gyur ba mi mnga' ba de bdag cag la bden pa mngon sum du bstan par ci gnang /
NK002(kha)011:1204: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po 'phags pa
NK002(kha)011:1205: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa thugs dri ma dang
NK002(kha)011:1206: skyon thams cad dang bral ba /
NK002(kha)011:1207: sku yon tan dri ma med pa'i tshogs kyi 'od zer gyis brgyan pa /
NK002(kha)011:1208: zhabs rten gyi pad+ma la lha dang mi dang lha
NK002(kha)011:1209: ma yin dang klu dang rig sngags 'chang rnams kyi
NK002(kha)011:1210: thor tshugs dang cod pan gyis gtugs pa /
NK002(kha)011:1211: ngan song gi 'gro ba sna tshogs 'dzom pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK002(kha)011:1214: skabs 'dir mchod pa ci 'byor pa dbul /
NK002(kha)011:1215: bcom ldan 'das 'phags pa 'jam dpal dus ngan pa'i
NK002(kha)011:1216: sems can las kyi sgrib pa sna tshogs kyis sgribs
NK002(kha)011:1217: pa / nad sna tshogs kyis gzir ba /
NK002(kha)011:1218: mya ngan dang sdug bsngal sna tshogs kyi gtses pa /
NK002(kha)011:1219: lta ba ngan pa sna tshogs kyis yongs su bsgribs pa /
NK002(kha)011:1220: lam dang sa dman par 'og nas 'og tu lhung
NK002(kha)011:1221: bar 'gyur ba'i sems can rnams la thugs brtse bar
NK002(kha)011:1222: dgongs te gang thos pa tsam gyis ci nas kyang
NK002(kha)011:1223: bla na med pa'i byang chub las phyir mi ldog
NK002(kha)011:1224: par 'gyur ba dang sdig pa dang las kyi sgrib
NK002(kha)011:1225: pa thams cad yongs su byang zhing bde bar 'gyur
NK002(kha)011:1226: ba dang bdud sdig can gyis mi bardzi bar 'gyur
NK002(kha)011:1227: ba dang / gnod pa dang mi bde ba tham
NK002(kha)011:1228: sa cad rab tu zhi bar 'gyur ba dang 'dod
NK002(kha)011:1229: dgu'i re ba rdzogs shing bsam pa thams cad yid
NK002(kha)011:1230: bzhin du 'grub par 'gyur ba'i de bzhin gshegs pa
NK002(kha)011:1231: bdun gyi mtshan dang sngon gyi smon lam gyi khyad
NK002(kha)011:1233: ston pa bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa la dmigs
NK002(kha)011:1234: kyis zhu ba mdzad cing gdan 'dzom pa'i dbus su
NK002(kha)011:1235: 'di skad ces bcom ldan 'das slad ma'i tshe slad
NK002(kha)011:1236: ma'i dus na / gang dag mdo sde 'di 'chang
NK002(kha)011:1237: ba dang gzhan dag la yang rgya cher yang dag
NK002(kha)011:1239: yi ger 'bri ba dang 'brir stsol ba dang glegs
NK002(kha)011:1240: bam du bris te me tog dang bdug pa dang
NK002(kha)011:1241: spos dang phreng ba dang byug pa dang gdugs dang
NK002(kha)011:1242: rgyal mtshan rnams kyis bkur stir bgyid pa'i rigs kyi
NK002(kha)011:1243: bu'am rigs kyi bu mo de dag la bdag gis
NK002(kha)011:1244: de bzhin gshegs pa sman gyi bla bee d+aur+ya'i 'od
NK002(kha)011:1245: kyi rgyal po de'i mtshan rnam pa sna tshogs su
NK002(kha)011:1246: bsgrag par bya'o // tha na rmi lam du yang
NK002(kha)011:1247: sangs rgyas kyi mtshan rna lam du nye bar bsgrag
NK002(kha)011:1248: bsgrag par bya'o // par bagyi'o // tshon sna lnga
NK002(kha)011:1249: pa'i ras kyis dkris te phyogs gtsang mar bzhag na
NK002(kha)011:1250: gang na mdo sde 'di gnas pa der rgyal po
NK002(kha)011:1251: chen po bzhi 'khor dang bcas pa dang lha bye
NK002(kha)011:1252: ba khrag khrig brgya stong gzhan yang mchis par 'gyur
NK002(kha)011:1253: bsgrag par bya'o // par bagyi'o // / mdo sde
NK002(kha)011:1254: 'dzin pa de dag dus ma lags bar 'chi bar
NK002(kha)011:1255: bsgrag par bya'o // par bagyi'o // / mi 'gyur
NK002(kha)011:1256: / sus kyang mdangs 'phrog par mi nus te 'phrog
NK002(kha)011:1257: na yang slar 'phrog par 'gyur ro zhes bgyi ba
NK002(kha)011:1258: la sogs pa gsungs shing 'phags pa'i bka' yang dag
NK002(kha)011:1259: pa tshad mar gyur pas zhal gyis bzhes pa bzhin
NK002(kha)011:1260: du deng 'dir yang mchod pa'i tshogs sbyar ba'i pho
NK002(kha)011:1261: brang gi dkyil 'khor 'dir bzhugs te mchod pa bzhes
NK002(kha)011:1262: shing de bzhin gshegs pa gdan 'dzom pa la thugs
NK002(kha)011:1263: dam las glongs te bskul ba dang /
NK002(kha)011:1264: mdo sde'i cho ga rdzogs par bskang ba'i phrin las
NK002(kha)011:1265: mdzad de mdo sde'i phan yon ji skad bka' bstsal
NK002(kha)011:1266: pa thams cad bdag cag la sogs pa sems can
NK002(kha)011:1267: thams cad kyis 'phral du thob par byin gyis brlabs
NK002(kha)011:1269: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po 'phags pa skyabs grol la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK002(kha)011:1272: skabs 'dir mchod pa ci 'byor pa dbul /
NK002(kha)011:1273: bcom ldan 'das 'phags pa skyabs grol dus ngan pa'i
NK002(kha)011:1274: sems can phongs shing sdug bsngal ba rnams la thugs
NK002(kha)011:1275: rtse bar dgongs te ston pa bcom ldan 'das gdan
NK002(kha)011:1276: 'dzom pa'i spyan sngar 'di skad du btsun pa bcom
NK002(kha)011:1277: ldan 'das slad ma'i tshe slad ma'i dus na sems
NK002(kha)011:1278: can bro nad sna tshogs kyis lus yongs su gzir
NK002(kha)011:1279: te / yun ring por bro nad kyis lus kyi
NK002(kha)011:1280: sha srab shing bkres pa dang skom pas gre ba
NK002(kha)011:1282: 'gum pa la ni mngon du phyogs /
NK002(kha)011:1283: mdza' bshes dang nye du dang snag gi gnyen mtshams ngu ba rnams kyis ni bskor /
NK002(kha)011:1284: phyogs rnams ni mun par mthong /
NK002(kha)011:1285: gshin rje'i mi rnams kyis ni drangs te de'i lus
NK002(kha)011:1286: 'di na nyal yang rnam par shes pa chos kyi
NK002(kha)011:1287: rgyal po gshin rje'i mdun du khrid cing mi de
NK002(kha)011:1288: dang lhan cig skyes pa'i lha slad bzhin 'brang ba
NK002(kha)011:1289: gang lags pa des dge ba'am mi dge ba bgyis
NK002(kha)011:1290: pa de dag thams cad legs par yi ger bris
NK002(kha)011:1291: nas chos kyi rgyal po gshin rje la phul ba
NK002(kha)011:1292: dang chos kyi rgyal po gshin rjes de la dris
NK002(kha)011:1293: shing brtags nas dge ba'am mi dge ba ji ltar
NK002(kha)011:1294: bgyis pa de bzhin du bsgo ba la /
NK002(kha)011:1295: gang dag nad pa de'i don du bcom ldan 'das
NK002(kha)011:1296: de bzhin gshegs pa sman gyi bla bee d+aur+ya'i 'od
NK002(kha)011:1297: kyi rgyal po de la skyabs su mchi zhing 'di
NK002(kha)011:1298: 'dra ba'i sbyor bas mchod par bgyid na de'i rnam
NK002(kha)011:1299: par shes pa slar ldog cing rmi lam rmis pa
NK002(kha)011:1300: bzhin du bdag nyid kyis 'tshal ba'i gnas der mchis
NK002(kha)011:1301: te yang na ni gdugs bdun /
NK002(kha)011:1302: yang ni gdugs nyi shu rtsa gcig /
NK002(kha)011:1303: yang na ni gdugs sum cu rtsa lnga /
NK002(kha)011:1304: yang na ni gdugs bzhi bcu rtsa dgu la de'i
NK002(kha)011:1305: rnam phar shes pa slar ldog cing dran pa rnyed
NK002(kha)011:1306: la dge ba dang mi dge ba'i las kyi rnam
NK002(kha)011:1307: par smin pa bdag nyid kyi mngon sum du 'gyur
NK002(kha)011:1308: te srog gi slad du yang sdig pa'i las mi
NK002(kha)011:1309: bgyid do // mchod pa'i sbyor ba ni btsun pa
NK002(kha)011:1310: kun dga' bo gang dag nad chen po las yongs
NK002(kha)011:1311: su thar bar 'dod pa de dag gis nad pa
NK002(kha)011:1312: de'i don du nyin bdun mtshan bdun du yan lag
NK002(kha)011:1313: brgyad dang ldan pa'i gso sbyong gi sdom pa blang
NK002(kha)011:1314: bgyid do // bar bya / dge slong gi dge
NK002(kha)011:1315: 'dun la zas dang skom rnams dang yo byad thams
NK002(kha)011:1316: cad kyis ci nus su mchod pa dang rim gro
NK002(kha)011:1317: bgyid do // bar bya / bya / nyin lan
NK002(kha)011:1318: gsum mtshan lan gsum du bcom ldan 'das de bzhin
NK002(kha)011:1319: gshegs pa sman gyi bla bee d+aur+ya'i 'od kyi rgyal
NK002(kha)011:1320: po de'i mtshan yid la bya /
NK002(kha)011:1321: mdo sde 'di yang lan bzhi bcu rtsa dgur 'don par bya'o //
NK002(kha)011:1322: zhag bzhi bcu rtsa dgur mer me 'bud par bya'o //
NK002(kha)011:1324: sku gzugs re re'i spyan sngar mar me bdun bdun bzhag /
NK002(kha)011:1325: mar me re re'i tshad kyang shing rta'i 'phang lo
NK002(kha)011:1326: tsam du byas te ci nas kyang zhag bzhi bcu
NK002(kha)011:1327: rtsa dgur mar me mi zad par bya'o //
NK002(kha)011:1328: tshon sna lnga ba'i ba dan bzhi bcu rtsa dgu las lhag par bya'o //
NK002(kha)011:1329: btsun pa kun dga' bo rgyal po rgyal rigs spyi
NK002(kha)011:1330: bo nas dbang bskur ba rnams la nad kyi gnod
NK002(kha)011:1331: pa dang rang ngam pha rol gyi dmag tshogs kyi
NK002(kha)011:1332: gnod pa'i rgyu skar ram gza' zla ba'am nyi ma'i
NK002(kha)011:1333: gnod pa'am dus ma yin pa'i rlung ngam char ram
NK002(kha)011:1334: than pa'i gnod pa yang rung /
NK002(kha)011:1335: gnod pa dang nad 'go ba'am 'khrug pa zhig nye bar gnas par gyur na /
NK002(kha)011:1336: rgyal po rgyal rigs spyi bo nas dbang bskur ba
NK002(kha)011:1337: des sems can thams cad la byams pa'i sems su
NK002(kha)011:1338: bya / btson du bzung ba rnams gtang bar bya
NK002(kha)011:1339: zhing gong du smos pa bzhin du bcom ldan 'das
NK002(kha)011:1340: sman gyi bla bee d+aur+ya'i 'od kyi rgyal po de
NK002(kha)011:1341: la de lta bu'i mchod pa byas na /
NK002(kha)011:1342: rgyal po de'i dge ba'i rtsa ba dang bcom ldan
NK002(kha)011:1343: 'das sman gyi bla bee d+aur+ya'i 'od kyi rgyal po
NK002(kha)011:1344: de'i sngon gyi smon lam gyi khyad par gyis yul
NK002(kha)011:1345: bde ba dang lo legs pa dang char dang rlung
NK002(kha)011:1346: dus su ldang zhing lo tog 'grub par 'gyur /
NK002(kha)011:1347: yul de na gnas pa'i sems can thams cad kyang
NK002(kha)011:1348: nad med pa dang bde ba dang mchog tu dga'
NK002(kha)011:1350: yul der gnod sbyin dang srin po dang 'byung po
NK002(kha)011:1351: dang sha za ma rung pas sems can rnams la
NK002(kha)011:1353: ltas ngan pa thams cad mthong bar mi 'gyur /
NK002(kha)011:1354: rgyal po de'i tshe dang mdog dang stobs dang nad
NK002(kha)011:1355: med pa dang dbang phyug rnams mngon par 'phel bar
NK002(kha)011:1356: 'gyur ro zhes bgyi ba la sogs pa bka' bstsal
NK002(kha)011:1357: pa gsung shing 'phags pa'i bka' yang dag pa tshad
NK002(kha)011:1358: mar gyur pas zhal gyis bzhes pa bzhin du deng
NK002(kha)011:1359: 'dir yang mchod pa'i tshogs sbyar ba'i pho brang gi
NK002(kha)011:1360: dkyil 'khor 'dir bzhugs te mchod pa bzhes shing de
NK002(kha)011:1361: bzhin gshegs pa gdan 'dzom pa la thugs dam las
NK002(kha)011:1362: glengs te bskul ba dang mdo sde'i cho ga rdzogs
NK002(kha)011:1363: par bskang ba'i 'phrin las mdzad de /
NK002(kha)011:1364: mdo sde 'di las phan yon ji skad bka' bstsal
NK002(kha)011:1365: pa thams cad bdag cag la sogs pa sems can
NK002(kha)011:1366: thams cad kyis thob par byin gyis rlabs cing bstsal
NK002(kha)011:1367: par ci gnang / byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa'
NK002(kha)011:1368: chen po phyag na rdo rje la phyag 'tshal lo
NK002(kha)011:1369: par ci gnang / // mchod do skyabs su mchi'o //
NK002(kha)011:1370: tshangs pa dang lha'i dbang po brgya byin dang rgyal
NK002(kha)011:1371: po chen po yul 'khor srung dang 'phags skyes po
NK002(kha)011:1372: dang mig mi bzang dang ku be ra la sogs
NK002(kha)011:1373: pa dam pa'i chos skyong ba'i lha'i dge bsnyen thams
NK002(kha)011:1377: skabs 'dir mchod pa ci 'byor pa dbul /
NK002(kha)011:1378: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po phyag na
NK002(kha)011:1379: rdo rje dang tshangs pa dang lha'i dbang po brgya
NK002(kha)011:1380: byin dang rgyal po chen po yul 'khor srung dang
NK002(kha)011:1381: 'phags skyes po dang mig mi bzang dang ku be
NK002(kha)011:1382: ra la sogs pa dam pa'i chos skyong ba'i lha'i
NK002(kha)011:1383: dge bsnyen chen po rnams kyis ji ltar sngon gdan
NK002(kha)011:1384: 'dzom pa chen po'i spyan sngar lha'i dam tshig bden
NK002(kha)011:1385: par mdong gsol du gsung gcig kho nar 'di skad
NK002(kha)011:1386: ces bcom ldan 'das bdag cag gis de bzhin gshegs
NK002(kha)011:1387: pa bdun gyi sngon gyi smon lam gyi khyad par
NK002(kha)011:1388: rgyas pa yang thos de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyang
NK002(kha)011:1389: mngon du mthong ste mchod pa yang bgyis so //
NK002(kha)011:1390: yang bcom ldan 'das sa phyogs gang na de bzhin
NK002(kha)011:1391: gshegs pa rnams kyi mtshan dang gzungs kyi tshig 'di
NK002(kha)011:1392: dag spyod pa der bdag cag g.yog dang bcas te
NK002(kha)011:1393: mchis par bagyi'o // rigs kyi bu'am /
NK002(kha)011:1394: rigs kyi bu mo gang zhig 'chang ba dang klog
NK002(kha)011:1395: pa dang mchod par bgyid pa dang yi ger 'brir
NK002(kha)011:1396: rtsol ba der bdag cag mthun par lhan cig tu
NK002(kha)011:1397: mchis te / rigs kyi bu'am rigs kyi bu mo'am
NK002(kha)011:1398: rgyal po'am rgyal po'i blon po mdo sde'i dbang po
NK002(kha)011:1399: 'dzin pa dang 'bri ba de la de bzhin gshegs
NK002(kha)011:1400: pa'i byin gyis brlabs kyis bsrung bar bagyi'o //
NK002(kha)011:1401: grong dang grong khyer dang phyogs kyang yongs su bskyangs bar bagyi'o //
NK002(kha)011:1403: dgra dang dgon pa'i gnod pa dang nad thams cad rab tu zhi bar 'agyi'o //
NK002(kha)011:1404: bdag cag ni de bzhin gshegs pa dang sems can thams cad la byams pa /
NK002(kha)011:1405: byas pa bzo ba lags te dus ma lags par 'gum pa thams cad bzlog par bagyi'o //
NK002(kha)011:1408: 'gyed pa thams cad rab tu zhi bar bagyi'o //
NK002(kha)011:1409: ji ltar bsam pa yid bzhin du 'grub pa dang
NK002(kha)011:1410: sems dang lus bde zhing longs spyod dang dbang phyug
NK002(kha)011:1411: dang nor dang 'bru rnams 'phel bar bagyi'o //
NK002(kha)011:1412: thams cad du bsrung bar bagyi'o //
NK002(kha)011:1413: bcom ldan 'das bdag cag rang gis bro bor ba
NK002(kha)011:1414: dang dam bcas pa 'di dag rigs kyi bu'am rigs
NK002(kha)011:1415: kyi bu mo des rjes su dran par bagyi'o //
NK002(kha)011:1417: a g+hu ma g+hu ta ra g+hu /
NK002(kha)011:1421: dzu dzu re dzu re swa h+aa //
NK002(kha)011:1422: gang la la zhig de bzhin gshegs pa'i mtshan rnams
NK002(kha)011:1423: dang gzungs kyi tshig 'di dag 'chang ba dang klog
NK002(kha)011:1424: pa dang yi ger 'bri ba dang yi ger 'brir
NK002(kha)011:1425: stsal ba dang rab tu gus pas mchod par bgyid
NK002(kha)011:1426: pa de dag ngan song gsum du mi 'chi bar
NK002(kha)011:1427: rig par bgyis te de ni bla na med pa
NK002(kha)011:1428: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas las slar mi
NK002(kha)011:1429: ldog par 'gyur / ji ltar 'tshal ba'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing de dag tu skye bar 'gyur /
NK002(kha)011:1430: de bzhin gshegs pa mthong bar 'gyur /
NK002(kha)011:1432: ting nge 'dzin dang gzungs kyang thob par 'gyur ro zhes gsungs shing zhal gyis bzhes pa dang /
NK002(kha)011:1433: de nas byang chub sems dpa' phyag na rdo rjes
NK002(kha)011:1434: de bzhin gshegs pa de dag la 'di skad ces
NK002(kha)011:1435: gang mdo sde'i dbang po 'dzin pa de dag gi
NK002(kha)011:1436: don du bdag gis gzungs kyi gsang sngags kyi gzhi
NK002(kha)011:1437: rnams stsal bar bgyi yis sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das
NK002(kha)011:1438: rnams pa dag la dgongs su gsol /
NK002(kha)011:1439: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas bdun po dag la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK002(kha)011:1440: rdo rje 'dzin pa thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK002(kha)011:1444: mchog lter rdo rje rdo rje ma /
NK002(kha)011:1446: rdo rje zhags 'dzin badz+re p+aa sh+aa d+ha ri ni /
NK002(kha)011:1449: kun nas mnyam zhing mnyam pa ma /
NK002(kha)011:1451: a pra ti ha ta badz+re /
NK002(kha)011:1452: thogs pa med pa'i rdo rje mas /
NK002(kha)011:1454: zhi ba zhi ba rab zhi bar /
NK002(kha)011:1456: sarba mdzod cig nad rnams thams cad pa b+y+aa d+ha
NK002(kha)011:1457: yah ku ru las rnams thams cad mdzod cig mdzod
NK002(kha)011:1459: bcom ldan dam tshig rjes dran pa'i /
NK002(kha)011:1460: sa ma ya ma nu sma ra b+ha ga w+aan /
NK002(kha)011:1461: phyag na rdo rje bdag gi ni /
NK002(kha)011:1463: bsam kun rdzogs pa'i gzhi tshugs shing /
NK002(kha)011:1464: sarba +aa sh+aa me pa ri p+au ra ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK002(kha)011:1465: bcom ldan 'das gang la la zhig de bzhin gshegs
NK002(kha)011:1466: pa 'di dag gi mtshan dang sngon gyi smon lam
NK002(kha)011:1467: gyi khyad par rgyas pa dang chos kyi rnam grangs
NK002(kha)011:1468: 'di 'chang ba dang klog pa de'i re ba thams
NK002(kha)011:1469: cad bdag gis yongs su bskang bar bagyi'o //
NK002(kha)011:1470: don thams cad yongs su bsgrub par bagyi'o //
NK002(kha)011:1471: gal te des bdag mthong bar 'tshal na chos kyi rnam grangs 'di yi ger 'brir stsal bar bgyi /
NK002(kha)011:1472: de bzhin gshegs pa 'di dag gi sku gzugs bdun yang bgyi /
NK002(kha)011:1473: rdo rje 'dzin yang sku gdung dang bcas par bgyi /
NK002(kha)011:1474: de bzhin gshegs pa de dag la yang ji skad
NK002(kha)011:1475: gong du smos pa bzhin du spos dang bdug pa
NK002(kha)011:1476: dang mar me dang phreng ba dang rgyan dang rol
NK002(kha)011:1477: mo'i sgra dang sil snyan dang pheg rdob pa rnams
NK002(kha)011:1478: kyis mchod de bskor bar bgyi /
NK002(kha)011:1479: gzungs kyi gsang sngags kyi gzhi 'di dag kyang gdon par bgyi /
NK002(kha)011:1480: sems can thams cad la yang phan pa'i sems dang byams pa'i sems su bgyi /
NK002(kha)011:1481: 'phags pa'i lam yan lag brgyad pa'i bsnyen gnas la
NK002(kha)011:1482: gnas te lan gsum khrus bgyi zhing gos lan gsum
NK002(kha)011:1483: barje bar bgyi / tshes brgyad nas brtsams te zla
NK002(kha)011:1484: ba phyi ma'i bco lnga nya'i bar du nyin gcig
NK002(kha)011:1485: bzhin rig sngags lan brgya rtsa brgyad bzlas na de
NK002(kha)011:1486: la bdag gis rmi lam du mthong ba bstsal bar
NK002(kha)011:1487: bgyi 'bel ba'i bka' mchid kyang bgyi /
NK002(kha)011:1488: re ba thams cad kyang yongs su bskang bar bagyi'o
NK002(kha)011:1489: zhes bya ba la sogs pa 'phags pa'i bka' mi
NK002(kha)011:1490: 'gyur ba tshad mar gyur bas zhal gyis bzhes pa
NK002(kha)011:1491: bzhin du ding 'dir yang mchod pa'i tshogs sbyar ba'i
NK002(kha)011:1492: pho brang gi dkyil 'khor 'dir bzhugs te mchod pa
NK002(kha)011:1493: bzhes shing gdan 'dzom pas mdo sde'i cho ga yongs
NK002(kha)011:1494: su rdzogs par bskang ba'i phrin las mdzad de phan
NK002(kha)011:1495: yon ji skad bka' bstsal pa thams cad bdag cag
NK002(kha)011:1496: la sogs pa sems can thams cad kyis thob par
NK002(kha)011:1497: byin gyis brlabs par ci gnang /
NK002(kha)011:1498: lhag par yang de bzhin gshegs pa bdun gyi sngon
NK002(kha)011:1499: gyi smon lam gyi khyad par rgyas pa'i mdo la
NK002(kha)011:1500: sogs pa gsung rab dam pa'i chos yun ring du
NK002(kha)011:1502: sgo thams cad nas chos spyod pa rnams la bar
NK002(kha)011:1503: chad dang bgegs su gyur pa dang bdud kyi phyogs
NK002(kha)011:1504: su gyur pa thams cad yul phyogs su mi nad
NK002(kha)011:1505: dang phyugs nad gtong ba dang than pa dang sad
NK002(kha)011:1506: dang ser ba la sogs pas lo log ma rungs
NK002(kha)011:1507: bar bgyid pa dang gnod pa dang mtshan ma ngan
NK002(kha)011:1508: pa dang bkra mi shis pa mang po ston cing
NK002(kha)011:1509: sems can la sdang bar sems pa'i gdon bgegs rigs
NK002(kha)011:1510: tha dad pa mang po yul phyogs 'di na rgyu
NK002(kha)011:1511: zhing gnas pa ci mchis pa thams cad dang /
NK002(kha)011:1512: che ge mo la sogs pa la sngon gyi las
NK002(kha)011:1513: kyis bdas pa'am 'phral gyi rkyen la sa byung ba'am
NK002(kha)011:1514: yul phyogs dang pha tshan dang rigs brgyud kyi sri
NK002(kha)011:1515: can du gyur pa yang rung ste /
NK002(kha)011:1516: che ge mo'i lus dang srog dang chab srid dang
NK002(kha)011:1517: dbang phyug dang 'khor dang yo byad la sogs pa
NK002(kha)011:1518: gang yang rung ba la ci yang rung ba'i sgo
NK002(kha)011:1519: nas gnod pa bgyid pa'i gdon bgegs ci mchis pa
NK002(kha)011:1520: thams cad gang la gang 'tshams ba'i thabs kyis 'dul
NK002(kha)011:1521: zhing 'khon dang gnod pa'i bsam pa 'dor du stsal
NK002(kha)011:1522: te zhi ba dang dge ba dang byams pa'i bsam
NK002(kha)011:1523: pa can du 'gyur zhing sngon chad bkra mi shis
NK002(kha)011:1524: pa dang gnod pa'i sbyor ba ngan pa bgyis pa
NK002(kha)011:1526: slan chad kyang gnod pa'i bag cing mi bgyid par
NK002(kha)011:1527: so so'i rigs kyi bro dam pos bsgag cing gdan
NK002(kha)011:1528: 'dzom pa'i spyan sngar dam tshig chen po bstsal ba'i
NK002(kha)011:1529: phrin las mdzad par ci gnang /
NK002(kha)011:1530: mthu dpal dang ldan pa'i dge bsnyen bcu gnyis la
NK002(kha)011:1531: gnod sbyin gyi sde dpon chen po ji 'jigs la
NK002(kha)011:1532: phyag 'tshal lo // mchod do skyabs su mchi'o //
NK002(kha)011:1533: gnod sbyin gyi sde dpon chen po rdo rje la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK002(kha)011:1535: gnod sbyin gyi sde dpon chen po rgyan 'dzin la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK002(kha)011:1537: gnod sbyin gyi sde dpon chen po gza' 'dzin la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK002(kha)011:1539: gnod sbyin gyi sde dpon chen po rlung 'dzin la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK002(kha)011:1541: gnod sbyin gyi sde dpon chen po gnas bcas la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK002(kha)011:1543: gnod sbyin gyi sde dpon chen po dbang 'dzin la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK002(kha)011:1545: gnod sbyin gyi sde dpon chen po btung 'dzin la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK002(kha)011:1547: gnod sbyin gyi sde dpon chen po smra 'dzin la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK002(kha)011:1549: gnod sbyin gyi sde dpon chen po bsam 'dzin la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK002(kha)011:1551: gnod sbyin gyi sde dpon chen po g.yo ba 'dzin la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK002(kha)011:1553: gnod sbyin gyi sde dpon chen po rdzogs byed la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK002(kha)011:1557: mthu dpal dang ldan pa'i dge bsnyen gnod sbyin gyi
NK002(kha)011:1558: sde dpon chen po bcu gnyis po re re la
NK002(kha)011:1559: g.yog 'khor gnod sbyin bdun 'bum bdun 'bum dang bcas
NK002(kha)011:1560: pa rnams la dgongs su gsol /
NK002(kha)011:1561: ji ltar sngon gdan 'dzom pa'i spyan sngar lha'i ngag
NK002(kha)011:1562: bden pas gsung gcig tu 'di skad du sangs rgyas
NK002(kha)011:1563: kyi mthus / bdag cag gi de bzhin gshegs pa
NK002(kha)011:1564: sman gyi bla bee d+au r+ya'i 'od kyi rgyal po'i
NK002(kha)011:1565: mtshan thos te bdag cag la yang ngan 'gror 'gro
NK002(kha)011:1567: des na bdag cag lhan cig tu mthun par ji
NK002(kha)011:1568: srid 'tsho'i bar du sangs rgyas la skyabs su mchi'o
NK002(kha)011:1571: sems can thams cad kyi don dang sman pa dang bde ba'i slad du spro bar bagyi'o //
NK002(kha)011:1572: bye brag tu grong ngam grong khyer ram grong rdal
NK002(kha)011:1573: lam dgon pa'i gnas gang na mdo sde 'di spyod
NK002(kha)011:1574: pa dang gang na de bzhin gshegs pa sman gyi
NK002(kha)011:1575: bla bee d+aur+ya'i 'od kyi rgyal po de'i mtshan 'chang
NK002(kha)011:1576: ba dang mchod pa dang rim gro byed pa'i sems
NK002(kha)011:1577: can de dag la bdag cag gis bsrung bar bgyi
NK002(kha)011:1579: gnod pa thams cad las yongs su thar bar bgyi /
NK002(kha)011:1580: bsam pa thams cad yongs su rdzogs par bagyi'o zhes
NK002(kha)011:1581: zhal gyi bzhes te thugs dam du bzhes shing bcom
NK002(kha)011:1582: ldan 'das kyis kyang gang gi phyir khyed de bzhin
NK002(kha)011:1583: gshegs pa sman gyi bla bee d+aur+ya'i 'od kyi rgyal
NK002(kha)011:1584: po de la byas pa gzo zhing rjes su dran
NK002(kha)011:1585: la sems can thams cad la phan pa'i phyir bzhugs
NK002(kha)011:1586: pa legs so legs so zhes rjes su gnang ba
NK002(kha)011:1587: ston pa de bzhin du deng 'dir yang mchod pa'i
NK002(kha)011:1588: tshogs sbyar ba'i pho brang gi dkyil 'khor 'dir dul
NK002(kha)011:1589: zhing zhi ba'i 'khor dang ldan par byams pa dang
NK002(kha)011:1590: thugs brtse bas mchod pa bzhes shing mdo sde'i cho
NK002(kha)011:1591: ga yongs su rdzogs par bkang ba'i phrin las mdzad
NK002(kha)011:1592: de phan yon ji skad bka' bstsal pa thams cad
NK002(kha)011:1593: bdag cag la sogs pa sems can thams cad kyis
NK002(kha)011:1594: thob par byin gyis brlabs par ci gnang /
NK002(kha)011:1595: lhag par yang de bzhin gshegs pa bdun gyi sngon
NK002(kha)011:1596: gyi smon lam gyi khyad par rgyas pa'i mdo la
NK002(kha)011:1597: sogs pa gsung rab dam pa'i chos yun ring du
NK002(kha)011:1598: rgyas par bgyi ba dang sgo thams cad nas chos
NK002(kha)011:1599: spyod pa rnams la bar chad dang bgegs su gyur
NK002(kha)011:1600: pa dang bdud kyi phyogs su gyur pa thams cad
NK002(kha)011:1601: dang yul phyogs su mi nad dang phyugs nad gtong
NK002(kha)011:1602: ba dang than pa dang sad dang ser ba la
NK002(kha)011:1603: sogs pas lo thog ma rungs bar bgyid pa dang
NK002(kha)011:1604: gnod pa dang mtshan ma ngan pa dang bkra mi
NK002(kha)011:1605: shis pa mang po ston cing sems can la sdang
NK002(kha)011:1606: bar sems pa'i gdon bgegs rigs tha dad pa mang
NK002(kha)011:1607: po yul khams dang yul phyogs 'dir rgyu ba mchis
NK002(kha)011:1608: so 'tshal dang / che ge mo la sngon gyi
NK002(kha)011:1609: las kyis bdas pa'am 'phral gyi rkyen las gyur pa'i
NK002(kha)011:1610: ma yul phyogs dang pha tshan dang rigs brgyud kyi
NK002(kha)011:1611: sri can du gyur pa yang rung ste che ge
NK002(kha)011:1612: mo'i lus dang srog dang chab srid dang dbang phyug
NK002(kha)011:1613: dang 'khor dang yo byad la sogs pa gang yang
NK002(kha)011:1614: rung ba la ci yang rung ba'i sgo nas gnod
NK002(kha)011:1615: pa bgyid pa'i gdon bgegs ci mchis pa thams cad
NK002(kha)011:1616: gang la gang 'dul ba'i thabs kyis gdul zhing 'khon
NK002(kha)011:1617: dang gnod pa'i bsam pa 'dor du stsal te zhi
NK002(kha)011:1618: ba dang dge ba dang byams pa'i bsam pa can
NK002(kha)011:1619: du bgyi zhing sngon chad bkra mi shis pa dang
NK002(kha)011:1620: gnod pa'i sbyor ba ngan pa bgyis pa rnams kyang
NK002(kha)011:1622: slan chad kyang gnod pa'i bag ci yang mi bgyid
NK002(kha)011:1623: par so so'i rigs kyi bro dam pos bsgag cing
NK002(kha)011:1624: gdan 'dzom pa'i spyan sngar dam tshig chen po stsal
NK002(kha)011:1625: ba'i phrin las mdzad par ci gnang /
NK002(kha)011:1626: re re nas mchod pa dbul zhing smon lam gdab
NK002(kha)011:1627: pa rdzogs pa'i skabs 'dir gzungs sngags bzlas la khrus
NK002(kha)011:1628: bya / 'phags pa gdan 'dzom pa la spyir mchod
NK002(kha)011:1629: pa ci 'byor pa dbul de bzhin gshegs pa bdun
NK002(kha)011:1630: gyi sngon gyi smon lam gyi khyad par rgyas pa'i
NK002(kha)011:1631: mdo sde las byung ba bzhin du mchod pa'i tshogs
NK002(kha)011:1632: sbyar ba'i pho brang gi dkyil 'khor 'dir /
NK002(kha)011:1633: de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par
NK002(kha)011:1634: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas bdun dang ston pa bcom ldan
NK002(kha)011:1635: 'das dpal sh+aakya thub pa 'khor dang bcas pa spyan
NK002(kha)011:1636: drangs nas mtshan nas brjod de phyag 'tshal ba dang
NK002(kha)011:1637: mchod cing / de dag sngon gyi smon lam khyad
NK002(kha)011:1638: par can dang mthun par smon lam btab pa dang
NK002(kha)011:1639: de dag gi spyan sngar sdig pa bshags pa dang
NK002(kha)011:1640: dge ba la rjes su yi rang ba dang bskul
NK002(kha)011:1641: zhing gsol ba btab pa la sogs pa'i bsod nams
NK002(kha)011:1642: ci mchis pa'i stobs dang de dag gi mthu dpal
NK002(kha)011:1643: dang byin gyis brlabs kyi stobs kyis 7 dkyus su
NK002(kha)011:1644: lha sras khri srong lde'u btsan gyis zhal snga nas
NK002(kha)011:1645: thog ma ma mchis pa'i 'khor ba nas bsags pa'i
NK002(kha)011:1646: sdig pa dang sgrib pa ci mnga' ba thams cad
NK002(kha)011:1648: sku la snyun mi mnga' zhing sku tshe bstan 'gro'i
NK002(kha)011:1649: phan bde'i rtsa lag tu gyur pa dbang phyug dam
NK002(kha)011:1650: pa rnams kyi zhes rgyal dbang lnga pas kha bsgyur
NK002(kha)011:1651: gnang ba ltar 'don pa ra 'di mchan /
NK002(kha)011:1652: 7ring ba dang dbu rmog btsan pa dang chab srid
NK002(kha)011:1653: 'jam dar che ba dang 'jig rten dang 'jig rten
NK002(kha)011:1654: las 'das pa'i dpal phun sum tshogs pa la mnga'
NK002(kha)011:1656: mthar yang tshogs gnyis yongs su rdzogs nas g.yung drung
NK002(kha)011:1657: gi sku chos kyi rgyal po sangs rgyas bcom ldan
NK002(kha)011:1658: 'das kyi go 'phang brnyes par gyur cig /
NK002(kha)011:1659: chab 'og tu gtogs pa'i 'bangs thams cad kyang phyi
NK002(kha)011:1660: nang gi gnod pa thams cad rab tu zhi zhing
NK002(kha)011:1661: bde skyid phun sum tshogs pa dang bla na med
NK002(kha)011:1662: pa'i byang chub chen po thob par gyur cig /
NK002(kha)011:1663: yul khams thams cad tu yang mi nad dang phyugs
NK002(kha)011:1664: nad dang lo nyes dang dgra'i gnod pa dang bkra
NK002(kha)011:1665: mi shis pa'i bag ci yang mi 'byung ba dang
NK002(kha)011:1666: char chu dus su bab ste lo phyugs 'phel zhing
NK002(kha)011:1667: rgyas pa dang bde skyid kyi dpal phun sum tshogs
NK002(kha)011:1668: pa dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK002(kha)011:1669: sems can thams cad kyang bde ba thams cad dang
NK002(kha)011:1670: ldan zhing 'jig rten gyi khams de dag tu skyes
NK002(kha)011:1671: nas sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das de rnams kyi zhal
NK002(kha)011:1672: mthong ste gdam ngag thob nas tshogs gnyis rdzogs nas
NK002(kha)011:1674: khyad par du yang dam pa'i chos yun ring du
NK002(kha)011:1675: gnas shing sgo thams cad nas dar zhing rgyas par
NK002(kha)011:1677: de nas bzod par gsol zhing gshegs su gsol lo //
NK002(kha)011:1678: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa
NK002(kha)011:1679: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas bdun 'khor dang
NK002(kha)011:1680: bcas pa dang ston pa bcom ldan 'das dpal sh+aakya
NK002(kha)011:1681: thub pa 'khor dang bcas pa gdan 'dzom pa'i spyan
NK002(kha)011:1682: sngar che ge mo la sogs pa 'gro ba mang
NK002(kha)011:1683: po'i don mdzad par gsol ba'i skabs 'dir /
NK002(kha)011:1684: bdag cag dus ngan pa'i sems can spyod pa dman
NK002(kha)011:1685: zhing ma dag pas ma 'tshal ba dang bag ma
NK002(kha)011:1686: mchis pa'i dbang gis lus ngag yid gsum gyi spyod
NK002(kha)011:1687: pa nyon mongs pa dang 'dres pa dang mchod pa'i
NK002(kha)011:1688: dngos po chung zhing ngan pa dang gtsang sbra ma
NK002(kha)011:1689: phyed pa dang mdo las byung ba'i cho ga bzhin
NK002(kha)011:1690: du ma lcogs pa la sogs pa 'khrul zhing nongs
NK002(kha)011:1691: pa thams cad 'phags pa thugs rje chen po dang
NK002(kha)011:1692: ldan pa rnams la bzod par gsol zhing mchis na
NK002(kha)011:1693: thugs rtse bar dgongs te bzod pa bzhes shing 'phral
NK002(kha)011:1694: du yun du bdag cag gi sgrib par mi 'gyur
NK002(kha)011:1695: bar byin gyis brlabs par ci gnang /
NK002(kha)011:1697: de nas gshegs su gsol ba ni /
NK002(kha)011:1698: khyed kyis sems can don kun mdzad //
NK002(kha)011:1699: rjes su mthun pa'i dngos grub stsol //
NK002(kha)011:1700: sangs rgyas yul du gshegs nas kyang //
NK002(kha)011:1701: slar yang thugs rjes 'byon par mdzod //
NK002(kha)011:1702: mgon po thugs rje chen po dang ldan pa rnams
NK002(kha)011:1703: kyis bdag cag dang sems can thams cad kyi don
NK002(kha)011:1705: so so'i zhing khams su rdzu 'phrul gyis 'khor dang bcas pa gshegs su gsol lo //
NK002(kha)011:1706: de bzhin gshegs pa bdun gyi sngon smon lam gyi
NK002(kha)011:1707: khyad par rgyas pa'i gzungs klag pa'i cho ga mdo
NK002(kha)011:1708: sde las btus pa slob dpon bo d+hi sa t+was
